      "content": "it’s really hard to tell if he's actually getting better or just tired. he's still looking a bit pale and that left side still looks a little awkward, but he's insistent that he just needs to sleep. i don't want to panic him and make him a huge deal out of nothing if it's just jet lag. are you sure it's not just the pressure from the flight? i'll just monitor him for a few more hours while he naps, right?",
